{"tid":806844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子海灘暢泳遇魔鬼魚 尾巴倒刺勾下體「男人最痛」","createTime":"2018-09-05T04:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T11:40:21.000Z","uid":122167,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"603cebc642d8bdd9b7e8edec30f40606f0794928","tid":806844,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:53:10.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】內地一名男子日前到海南三亞游泳時，不幸被魔鬼魚尾巴刺中下體，他立即爬上沙灘求救，大聲呼痛。據了解，男子除不斷喊痛外，意識十分清醒，救援人員替他急救後，他可自行起身。<br />\n<br />\n當地消防局表示，意外於上周六中午發生，有民眾報案稱有泳客遭魔鬼魚攻擊，傷及下體。消防員趕至現場後，發現男子是被魔鬼魚尾巴上的倒刺勾到生殖器官，遂用絕緣剪先將毒刺部分剪斷，再將其送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e091c81b2059f081b58666edd64e47241c648476","tid":806844,"uid":122167,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"補圖:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j15t6lyg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj15t6lyg&h=6ba62df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15ebc5da471c013e0515f433b1051917f410e466","tid":806844,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94737fcf2a393d418f2d4ee861682fcc0b8c2179","tid":806844,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"佢同條魚玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b8326583077416024865835bc0076e1d3555be","tid":806844,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94737fcf2a393d418f2d4ee861682fcc0b8c2179","tid":806844,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"佢同條魚玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"格劍輸左"},{"pid":"97ead02b9a68815757352a84dc4